{"pageid":77186,"pagename":"Shades of Mort'ton/Quick guide","title":"Shades of Mort'ton/Quick guide","displaytitle":"Shades of Mort'ton/Quick guide","revid":14271002,"redirects":["Shades of mort'ton/quick guide"],"properties":[{"name":"smw-semanticdata-status","value":""},{"name":"notoc","value":""},{"name":"description","value":"Quest complete!"}],"content":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"noexcerpt noprint nomobile navigation-not-searchable rs-external-header-links\" style=\"display:none\"><span class=\"rs-header-icon rs-header-icon-rs\" data-text=\"RuneScape\" data-title=\"The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on Shades of Mort&#39;ton/Quick guide.\" data-site=\"rs\">The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on: <a href=\"https://runescape.wiki/w/Shades_of_Mort%27ton/Quick_guide\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"rsw:Shades of Mort&#39;ton/Quick guide\">rsw:Shades of Mort'ton/Quick guide</a></span></div>\n<table class=\"messagebox\">\n<tbody><tr><td style=\"width: 50px;\"><div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><img alt=\"Instruction manual.png\" src=\"/images/Instruction_manual.png?13f14\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"28\" height=\"27\" data-file-width=\"28\" data-file-height=\"27\" /></div></div></td>\n<td><span class=\"messagebox-title\"><b>This quick guide has an <a href=\"/w/Shades_of_Mort%27ton\" title=\"Shades of Mort&#39;ton\">in-depth guide here</a>.</b></span><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><div style=\"font-size:0.85em; line-height:1.4em;\" class=\"messagebox-text\">It contains a more detailed description of dialogue, cutscenes, and storyline.\n</div></td>\n</tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Details\">Details</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Shades_of_Mort%27ton/Quick_guide?section=1&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Details\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Shades_of_Mort%27ton/Quick_guide?action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Details\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"questdetails plainlinks\" cellspacing=\"3\"><tbody><tr><th class=\"questdetails-header\">Start point</th><td class=\"questdetails-info\"><img alt=\"Quest point icon.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/Quest_point_icon.png/17px-Quest_point_icon.png?dc356\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"17\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"/images/Quest_point_icon.png?dc356 1.5x\" data-file-width=\"21\" data-file-height=\"21\" /> Find the <a href=\"/w/Diary_(Shades_of_Mort%27ton)\" title=\"Diary (Shades of Mort&#39;ton)\">Diary of Herbi Flax</a> on a shelf in a house on the south-west side of the village of Mort'ton.</td></tr><tr><th class=\"questdetails-header\">Official difficulty</th><td class=\"questdetails-info\">Intermediate</td></tr><tr><th class=\"questdetails-header\">Description</th><td class=\"questdetails-info\">The townsfolk of <a href=\"/w/Mort%27ton\" title=\"Mort&#39;ton\">Mort'ton</a> have some form of strange affliction and the town is full of Shades. Can you find some way to reverse this?</td></tr><tr><th class=\"questdetails-header\">Official length</th><td class=\"questdetails-info\">Short</td></tr><tr><th class=\"questdetails-header\">Requirements</th><td class=\"questdetails-info qc-input qc-active\">\n<ul><li>Completion of <a href=\"/w/Quest_points\" title=\"Quest points\"><img alt=\"Quest points\" src=\"/images/Quest_point_icon.png?dc356\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"21\" height=\"21\" data-file-width=\"21\" data-file-height=\"21\" /></a>  <a href=\"/w/Priest_in_Peril\" title=\"Priest in Peril\">Priest in Peril</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"scp\" data-skill=\"Crafting\" data-level=\"20\"><a href=\"/w/Crafting\" title=\"Crafting\"><img alt=\"Crafting\" src=\"/images/thumb/Crafting_icon.png/21px-Crafting_icon.png?a1f71\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"21\" height=\"19\" srcset=\"/images/Crafting_icon.png?a1f71 1.5x\" data-file-width=\"24\" data-file-height=\"22\" /></a> 20 <a href=\"/w/Crafting\" title=\"Crafting\">Crafting</a></span> <sup>(<span title=\"This requirement is boostable\" style=\"cursor:help; text-decoration: underline dotted;\">boostable</span>)</sup></li>\n<li><span class=\"scp\" data-skill=\"Herblore\" data-level=\"15\"><a href=\"/w/Herblore\" title=\"Herblore\"><img alt=\"Herblore\" src=\"/images/thumb/Herblore_icon.png/21px-Herblore_icon.png?ffa9e\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"21\" height=\"14\" srcset=\"/images/Herblore_icon.png?ffa9e 1.5x\" data-file-width=\"25\" data-file-height=\"17\" /></a> 15 <a href=\"/w/Herblore\" title=\"Herblore\">Herblore</a></span> <sup>(<span title=\"This requirement is boostable\" style=\"cursor:help; text-decoration: underline dotted;\">boostable</span>)</sup></li>\n<li><span class=\"scp\" data-skill=\"Firemaking\" data-level=\"5\"><a href=\"/w/Firemaking\" title=\"Firemaking\"><img alt=\"Firemaking\" src=\"/images/thumb/Firemaking_icon.png/21px-Firemaking_icon.png?45ea0\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"21\" height=\"21\" srcset=\"/images/Firemaking_icon.png?45ea0 1.5x\" data-file-width=\"23\" data-file-height=\"23\" /></a> 5 <a href=\"/w/Firemaking\" title=\"Firemaking\">Firemaking</a></span> <sup>(<span title=\"This requirement is boostable\" style=\"cursor:help; text-decoration: underline dotted;\">boostable</span>)</sup></li>\n<li>Must be able to defeat 5 level-40 <a href=\"/w/Loar_Shade\" title=\"Loar Shade\">Loar Shades</a>.</li>\n<li>Must be able to survive an onslaught when rebuilding the Temple, and being surrounded by many players makes this much easier.</li></ul></td></tr><tr><th class=\"questdetails-header\">Items required</th><td class=\"questdetails-info\">\n<div class=\"lighttable checklist no-toggle-parent\">\n<ul><li>5000+ <a href=\"/w/Coins\" title=\"Coins\">coins</a> (bring plenty of money just in case)</li>\n<li>2 <a href=\"/w/Tarromin_potion_(unf)\" title=\"Tarromin potion (unf)\">Tarromin potion (unf)</a> (made by adding 2 clean <a href=\"/w/Tarromin\" title=\"Tarromin\">Tarromins</a> (obtainable during quest) to 2 <a href=\"/w/Vial_of_water\" title=\"Vial of water\">vials of water</a> (empty vials are obtainable during quest))</li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Tinderbox\" title=\"Tinderbox\">Tinderbox</a></li>\n<li>An <a href=\"/w/Axe\" title=\"Axe\">axe</a> for cutting pyre logs</li>\n<li>2 <a href=\"/w/Ashes\" title=\"Ashes\">Ashes</a></li>\n<li>Prior to building the temple, you need a <a href=\"/w/Hammer\" title=\"Hammer\">hammer</a> (1 coin at the <a href=\"/w/General_store\" title=\"General store\">general store</a>). However, a regular hammer is insufficient to build the temple without a large group. An additional 13,000 coins (or <span class=\"coins coins-1000 coins-pos\">5,497</span> on the <a href=\"/w/Grand_Exchange\" title=\"Grand Exchange\">Grand Exchange</a>) allows you to buy a <a href=\"/w/Flamtaer_hammer\" title=\"Flamtaer hammer\">Flamtaer hammer</a>, which is necessary to complete this part of the <a href=\"/w/Quest\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Quest\">quest</a> without a group.</li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th class=\"questdetails-header\">Recommended</th><td class=\"questdetails-info qc-active\">\n<div class=\"lighttable checklist no-toggle-parent\">\n<ul><li><span class=\"scp\" data-skill=\"Combat level\" data-level=\"25\"><a href=\"/w/Combat_level\" title=\"Combat level\"><img alt=\"Combat level\" src=\"/images/Attack_style_icon.png?ceb2e\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"21\" height=\"21\" data-file-width=\"19\" data-file-height=\"19\" /></a> 25 <a href=\"/w/Combat_level\" title=\"Combat level\">Combat level</a></span></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Combat_equipment\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Combat equipment\">Combat equipment</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Food\" title=\"Food\">Food</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Mort%27ton_teleport\" title=\"Mort&#39;ton teleport\">Mort'ton teleport</a> scroll or <a href=\"/w/Barrows_teleport_(tablet)\" title=\"Barrows teleport (tablet)\">Barrows teleport tablet</a> to teleport to Mort'ton</li>\n<li>2 or 3 <a href=\"/w/Tarromin\" title=\"Tarromin\">tarromin</a> herbs, <a href=\"/w/Ashes\" title=\"Ashes\">ashes</a>, and spare <a href=\"/w/Logs\" title=\"Logs\">logs</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Druid_pouch\" title=\"Druid pouch\">Druid pouch</a> (only if travelling through the swamp with <a href=\"/w/Ghast\" title=\"Ghast\">ghasts</a>)</li>\n<li>1 to 4 <a href=\"/w/Flamtaer_bracelet\" title=\"Flamtaer bracelet\">Flamtaer bracelets</a> (HIGHLY recommended; the minigame is usually unpopulated)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Flamtaer_hammer\" title=\"Flamtaer hammer\">Flamtaer hammer</a> (HIGHLY recommended; the minigame is usually unpopulated)</li>\n<li>11 inventory slots</li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th class=\"questdetails-header\">Enemies to defeat</th><td class=\"questdetails-info\">\n<ul><li>5 <a href=\"/w/Loar_Shade\" title=\"Loar Shade\">Loar Shades</a> <i>(level 40)</i></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table><div class=\"hidden\" style=\"display:none\">&#123;&#34;requirements&#34;:&#34;* Completion of &#91;&#91;File:Quest point icon.png|21x21px|link&#61;Quest points|alt&#61;Quest points&#93;&#93;  &#91;&#91;Priest in Peril&#93;&#93;\\n* &#60;span class&#61;\\&#34;scp\\&#34; data-skill&#61;\\&#34;Crafting\\&#34; data-level&#61;\\&#34;20\\&#34;&#62;&#91;&#91;File:Crafting icon.png|21x21px|link&#61;Crafting|alt&#61;Crafting&#93;&#93; 20 &#91;&#91;Crafting&#93;&#93;&#60;/span&#62; &#60;sup&#62;(&#60;span title&#61;\\&#34;This requirement is boostable\\&#34; style&#61;\\&#34;cursor:help; text-decoration: underline dotted;\\&#34;&#62;boostable&#60;/span&#62;)&#60;/sup&#62;\\n* &#60;span class&#61;\\&#34;scp\\&#34; data-skill&#61;\\&#34;Herblore\\&#34; data-level&#61;\\&#34;15\\&#34;&#62;&#91;&#91;File:Herblore icon.png|21x21px|link&#61;Herblore|alt&#61;Herblore&#93;&#93; 15 &#91;&#91;Herblore&#93;&#93;&#60;/span&#62; &#60;sup&#62;(&#60;span title&#61;\\&#34;This requirement is boostable\\&#34; style&#61;\\&#34;cursor:help; text-decoration: underline dotted;\\&#34;&#62;boostable&#60;/span&#62;)&#60;/sup&#62;\\n* &#60;span class&#61;\\&#34;scp\\&#34; data-skill&#61;\\&#34;Firemaking\\&#34; data-level&#61;\\&#34;5\\&#34;&#62;&#91;&#91;File:Firemaking icon.png|21x21px|link&#61;Firemaking|alt&#61;Firemaking&#93;&#93; 5 &#91;&#91;Firemaking&#93;&#93;&#60;/span&#62; &#60;sup&#62;(&#60;span title&#61;\\&#34;This requirement is boostable\\&#34; style&#61;\\&#34;cursor:help; text-decoration: underline dotted;\\&#34;&#62;boostable&#60;/span&#62;)&#60;/sup&#62; \\n* Must be able to defeat 5 level-40 &#91;&#91;Loar Shade&#93;&#93;s.\\n* Must be able to survive an onslaught when rebuilding the Temple, and being surrounded by many players makes this much easier.&#34;,&#34;desc&#34;:&#34;The townsfolk of &#91;&#91;Mort&#39;ton&#93;&#93; have some form of strange affliction and the town is full of Shades. Can you find some way to reverse this?&#34;,&#34;difficulty&#34;:&#34;Intermediate&#34;,&#34;kills&#34;:&#34;* 5 &#91;&#91;Loar Shade&#93;&#93;s &#39;&#39;(level 40)&#39;&#39;&#34;,&#34;name&#34;:&#34;Shades of Mort&#39;ton/Quick guide&#34;,&#34;start&#34;:&#34;Find the &#91;&#91;Diary (Shades of Mort&#39;ton)|Diary of Herbi Flax&#93;&#93; on a shelf in a house on the south-west side of the village of Mort&#39;ton.&#34;,&#34;length&#34;:&#34;Short&#34;,&#34;items&#34;:&#34;* 5000+ &#91;&#91;coins&#93;&#93; (bring plenty of money just in case)\\n* 2 &#91;&#91;Tarromin potion (unf)&#93;&#93; (made by adding 2 clean &#91;&#91;Tarromin&#93;&#93;s (obtainable during quest) to 2 &#91;&#91;Vial of water|vials of water&#93;&#93; (empty vials are obtainable during quest))\\n* &#91;&#91;Tinderbox&#93;&#93;\\n* An &#91;&#91;axe&#93;&#93; for cutting pyre logs\\n* 2 &#91;&#91;Ashes&#93;&#93;\\n* Prior to building the temple, you need a &#91;&#91;hammer&#93;&#93; (1 coin at the &#91;&#91;general store&#93;&#93;). However, a regular hammer is insufficient to build the temple without a large group. An additional 13,000 coins (or &#60;span class&#61;\\&#34;coins coins-1000 coins-pos\\&#34;&#62;5,497&#60;/span&#62; on the &#91;&#91;Grand Exchange&#93;&#93;) allows you to buy a &#91;&#91;Flamtaer hammer&#93;&#93;, which is necessary to complete this part of the &#91;&#91;quest&#93;&#93; without a group.&#34;&#125;</div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Walkthrough\">Walkthrough</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Shades_of_Mort%27ton/Quick_guide?section=2&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Walkthrough\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Shades_of_Mort%27ton/Quick_guide?action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Walkthrough\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Start\">Start</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Shades_of_Mort%27ton/Quick_guide?section=3&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Start\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Shades_of_Mort%27ton/Quick_guide?action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Start\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"lighttable checklist\">\n<ul><li>Enter the ruined house in the south-west of <a href=\"/w/Mort%27ton\" title=\"Mort&#39;ton\">Mort'ton</a>. Search the shelf on the wall. <b>Read the diary</b>. After reading the diary, the quest is started and you are able to create <a href=\"/w/Serum_207\" title=\"Serum 207\">Serum 207</a>.</li>\n<li>If you didn't bring <a href=\"/w/Tarromin_potion_(unf)\" title=\"Tarromin potion (unf)\">Tarromin potion (unf)</a>: Pick up the empty vials (can be filled in the house north-east) and search the smashed table for 2 tarromin and one <a href=\"/w/Rogue%27s_purse\" title=\"Rogue&#39;s purse\">rogue's purse</a>.</li></ul>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Serum_207\">Serum 207</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Shades_of_Mort%27ton/Quick_guide?section=4&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Serum 207\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Shades_of_Mort%27ton/Quick_guide?action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Serum 207\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"lighttable checklist\">\n<ul><li>Make two <a href=\"/w/Serum_207\" title=\"Serum 207\">Serum 207</a> by adding clean tarromin to a vial of water and then adding ashes.</li>\n<li>Use one dose on <a href=\"/w/Razmire\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Razmire\">Razmire</a> (afflicted) in the general store. <span class=\"chat-options\">(<i title=\"Chat options\"><img alt=\"Chat\" src=\"/images/Quick_chat_button.png?cf91b\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"13\" height=\"10\" data-file-width=\"13\" data-file-height=\"10\" /></i> <span class=\"chat-options-underline\" title=\"What are all these shadowy creatures?\">4</span>&#8226;<span class=\"chat-options-underline\" title=\"Yes, I&#39;ll dispatch those dark and evil creatures.\">1</span>)</span><span class=\"hidden js-tooltip-click\" data-tooltip-name=\"c_option-837d87176101b726b451f1d503baa4b8\" style=\"display:none;color:grey;background:none;border:none\"><b>&#8230;</b></span><div class=\"hidden js-tooltip-wrapper\" data-tooltip-limit-width=\"yes\" data-tooltip-arrow-size=\"10\" data-tooltip-for=\"c_option-837d87176101b726b451f1d503baa4b8\" data-tooltip-arrow=\"yes\" style=\"display:none;padding:0\"><div class=\"js-tooltip-text\"><table><tbody><tr><td><b>4</b></td><td>What are all these shadowy creatures?</td></tr><tr><td><b>1</b></td><td>Yes, I'll dispatch those dark and evil creatures.</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div> (Recommended to <b>not</b> use official Mort'ton temple World 377 yet to not get interrupted talking to the NPCs, until the step with repairing.)</li>\n<li>Kill five loar shades and pick up their remains. <b>Note:</b> any shades that you killed before talking to Razmire will not count.</li>\n<li>Return to Razmire and give him the remains. He may require more Serum 207.</li>\n<li>Right click and open his General store, buy an Olive oil.</li>\n<li>Open his builders' store, buy 5 timber beams, 5 limestone bricks, 25 swamp paste and optionally a <a href=\"/w/Flamtaer_hammer\" title=\"Flamtaer hammer\">Flamtaer hammer</a>.</li>\n<li>Use the serum on <a href=\"/w/Ulsquire_Shauncy\" title=\"Ulsquire Shauncy\">Ulsquire Shauncy</a>, located in the house east of the general store. Talk to him with Loar Remains.</li>\n<li>Talk to him <b>again</b> and ask about the remains and the temple. <span class=\"chat-options\">(<i title=\"Chat options\"><img alt=\"Chat\" src=\"/images/Quick_chat_button.png?cf91b\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"13\" height=\"10\" data-file-width=\"13\" data-file-height=\"10\" /></i> <span class=\"chat-options-underline\" title=\"What did you find out about the remains?\">1</span>&#8226;<span class=\"chat-options-underline\" title=\"What can you tell me about that temple?\">2</span>)</span><span class=\"hidden js-tooltip-click\" data-tooltip-name=\"c_option-46a7c856198b809860f9f63aa5561a54\" style=\"display:none;color:grey;background:none;border:none\"><b>&#8230;</b></span><div class=\"hidden js-tooltip-wrapper\" data-tooltip-limit-width=\"yes\" data-tooltip-arrow-size=\"10\" data-tooltip-for=\"c_option-46a7c856198b809860f9f63aa5561a54\" data-tooltip-arrow=\"yes\" style=\"display:none;padding:0\"><div class=\"js-tooltip-text\"><table><tbody><tr><td><b>1</b></td><td>What did you find out about the remains?</td></tr><tr><td><b>2</b></td><td>What can you tell me about that temple?</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div></li></ul>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Repairing_the_temple\">Repairing the temple</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Shades_of_Mort%27ton/Quick_guide?section=5&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Repairing the temple\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Shades_of_Mort%27ton/Quick_guide?action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Repairing the temple\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"lighttable checklist\">\n<ul><li>Head north-east of Mort'ton and repair the temple until you reach 100% repair and at least 20 sanctity. (Recommended to use official world 377.)</li>\n<li>Light the sacred altar in the centre of the temple (or wait until someone else lights it if you don't have level 5 firemaking)</li>\n<li>Use your olive oil on the flame to make <a href=\"/w/Sacred_oil\" title=\"Sacred oil\">sacred oil</a>.</li>\n<li>(Recommended) Use Serum 207 on the flame to make <a href=\"/w/Serum_208\" title=\"Serum 208\">Serum 208</a>, which permanently cures NPCs.</li></ul>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Burning_a_shade\">Burning a shade</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Shades_of_Mort%27ton/Quick_guide?section=6&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Burning a shade\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Shades_of_Mort%27ton/Quick_guide?action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: Burning a shade\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"lighttable checklist\">\n<ul><li>Use the sacred oil on a log to create a <a href=\"/w/Pyre_logs\" title=\"Pyre logs\">pyre log</a>.</li>\n<li>Head west of Mort'ton general store, to any grouping of 4 stone funeral pyres. Use the pyre log, then Loar remains on a <a href=\"/w/Shades_of_Mort%27ton_(minigame)#Cremating_the_Shades\" title=\"Shades of Mort&#39;ton (minigame)\">funeral pyre</a>.</li>\n<li>Light the funeral pyre. <b>Warning</b>: This will grant 25 Prayer XP.</li>\n<li>Collect the reward.</li>\n<li>(Recommended) Use the Serum 208 on Razmire.</li>\n<li>Use the Serum 208 on Ulsquire and finish the dialogue.</li></ul>\n</div>\n<p><b>Quest complete!</b>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Rewards\">Rewards</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Shades_of_Mort%27ton/Quick_guide?section=7&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Rewards\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Shades_of_Mort%27ton/Quick_guide?action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: Rewards\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/w/File:Shades_of_Mort%27ton_reward_scroll.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Shades of Mort&#39;ton reward scroll.png\" src=\"/images/Shades_of_Mort%27ton_reward_scroll.png?72159\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"488\" height=\"320\" data-file-width=\"488\" data-file-height=\"320\" /></a></div></div>\n<ul><li>3 <a href=\"/w/Quest_points\" title=\"Quest points\"><img alt=\"Quest points\" src=\"/images/Quest_point_icon.png?dc356\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"21\" height=\"21\" data-file-width=\"21\" data-file-height=\"21\" /></a>  <a href=\"/w/Quest_points\" title=\"Quest points\">Quest points</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"scp\" data-skill=\"Herblore\" data-level=\"2,000\"><a href=\"/w/Herblore\" title=\"Herblore\"><img alt=\"Herblore\" src=\"/images/thumb/Herblore_icon.png/21px-Herblore_icon.png?ffa9e\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"21\" height=\"14\" srcset=\"/images/Herblore_icon.png?ffa9e 1.5x\" data-file-width=\"25\" data-file-height=\"17\" /></a> 2,000 </span> <a href=\"/w/Herblore\" title=\"Herblore\">Herblore</a> experience</li>\n<li><span class=\"scp\" data-skill=\"Crafting\" data-level=\"2,000\"><a href=\"/w/Crafting\" title=\"Crafting\"><img alt=\"Crafting\" src=\"/images/thumb/Crafting_icon.png/21px-Crafting_icon.png?a1f71\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"21\" height=\"19\" srcset=\"/images/Crafting_icon.png?a1f71 1.5x\" data-file-width=\"24\" data-file-height=\"22\" /></a> 2,000 </span> <a href=\"/w/Crafting\" title=\"Crafting\">Crafting</a> experience</li>\n<li>Ability to play the <a href=\"/w/Shades_of_Mort%27ton_(minigame)\" title=\"Shades of Mort&#39;ton (minigame)\">Shades of Mort'ton minigame</a></li>\n<li>Ability to use the Shades of Mort'ton <a href=\"/w/Minigame_teleport\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Minigame teleport\">minigame teleport</a></li>\n<li>Bonus: If you take the <a href=\"/w/Diary_(Shades_of_Mort%27ton)\" title=\"Diary (Shades of Mort&#39;ton)\">Diary of Herbi Flax</a> to the <a href=\"/w/Apothecary\" title=\"Apothecary\">Apothecary</a> in <a href=\"/w/Varrock\" title=\"Varrock\">Varrock</a>, you'll get an extra 335 <a href=\"/w/Herblore\" title=\"Herblore\">Herblore</a> experience (can only be done once).</li></ul>\n<table class=\"navbox nowraplinks mw-collapsible\" data-expandtext=\"show\" data-navbox-name=\"Shades of Mort&#39;ton\" data-collapsetext=\"hide\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" class=\"navbox-title\" id=\"navbox-title\"><div class=\"navbox-title-name-notplain\"><div class=\"navbar\" style=\"float:left;text-align:left;width:6em\"><div class=\"plainlinks noprint\" style=\"background-color:transparent;padding:0;font-weight:normal;font-size:xx-small;white-space:nowrap\"><a href=\"/w/Template:Shades_of_Mort%27ton\" title=\"Template:Shades of Mort&#39;ton\"><span title=\"View this template\">v</span></a>&#160;<span style=\"font-size:80%\">&#8226;</span>&#160;<a class=\"text\" href=\"https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Template_talk:Shades_of_Mort%27ton\"><span title=\"Discussion about this template\">d</span></a>&#160;<span style=\"font-size:80%\">&#8226;</span>&#1