alt=\"Diary (Shades of Mort&#39;ton).png\" src=\"/images/Diary_%28Shades_of_Mort%27ton%29.png?2c9d4\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"30\" height=\"29\" data-file-width=\"30\" data-file-height=\"29\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Diary_(Shades_of_Mort%27ton)\" title=\"Diary (Shades of Mort&#39;ton)\">Diary</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Serum_207\" title=\"Serum 207\"><img alt=\"Serum 207 (3).png\" src=\"/images/Serum_207_%283%29.png?c943f\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"21\" height=\"30\" data-file-width=\"21\" data-file-height=\"30\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Serum_207\" title=\"Serum 207\">Serum 207</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Serum_208\" title=\"Serum 208\"><img alt=\"Serum 208 (3).png\" src=\"/images/Serum_208_%283%29.png?4b960\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"21\" height=\"30\" data-file-width=\"21\" data-file-height=\"30\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Serum_208\" title=\"Serum 208\">Serum 208</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Olive_oil\" title=\"Olive oil\"><img alt=\"Olive oil(3).png\" src=\"/images/Olive_oil%283%29.png?56826\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"21\" height=\"30\" data-file-width=\"21\" data-file-height=\"30\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Olive_oil\" title=\"Olive oil\">Olive oil</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Sacred_oil\" title=\"Sacred oil\"><img alt=\"Sacred oil(3).png\" src=\"/images/Sacred_oil%283%29.png?2eee6\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"21\" height=\"30\" data-file-width=\"21\" data-file-height=\"30\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Sacred_oil\" title=\"Sacred oil\">Sacred oil</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Loar_remains\" title=\"Loar remains\"><img alt=\"Loar remains.png\" src=\"/images/Loar_remains.png?6dc61\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"29\" height=\"30\" data-file-width=\"29\" data-file-height=\"30\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Loar_remains\" title=\"Loar remains\">Loar remains</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Unfinished_potion\" title=\"Unfinished potion\"><img alt=\"Unfinished potion.png\" src=\"/images/Unfinished_potion.png?4a467\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"21\" height=\"30\" data-file-width=\"21\" data-file-height=\"30\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Unfinished_potion\" title=\"Unfinished potion\">Unfinished potion</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Locations</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/Mort%27ton\" title=\"Mort&#39;ton\">Mort'ton</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Flamtaer\" title=\"Flamtaer\">Flamtaer</a> <sup><a href=\"/w/Fire_altar_(Flamtaer)\" title=\"Fire altar (Flamtaer)\">Fire altar</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Shade_Catacombs\" title=\"Shade Catacombs\">Shade Catacombs</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Music</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/Lair\" title=\"Lair\">Lair</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Related</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/Shades_of_Mort%27ton_(minigame)\" title=\"Shades of Mort&#39;ton (minigame)\">Shades of Mort'ton (minigame)</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Quick Guide</a></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mediawiki‐7bfb498f95‐lgkzc\nCached time: 20220517161028\nCache expiry: 3600\nReduced expiry: true\nComplications: []\n[SMW] In‐text annotation parser time: 0.001 seconds\nCPU time usage: 0.201 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.264 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 494/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 33860/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 5198/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/100\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.017/10.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 1320729/367001600 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  209.362      1 -total\n 51.98%  108.830      1 Template:Quest_details_page\n 15.29%   32.020      1 Template:Quest_rewards_page\n 10.23%   21.415      4 Template:Checklist\n 10.08%   21.101      2 Template:Navbox\n  9.67%   20.250      1 Template:Shades_of_Mort'ton\n  8.89%   18.603      1 Template:External\n  4.84%   10.142      5 Template:Ctg\n  4.28%    8.963      2 Template:Chat_option\n  3.49%    7.301      1 Template:Quick_Guide\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key en_osrswiki:pcache:idhash:77186-0!canonical and timestamp 20220517161028 and revision id 14271002. Serialized with PHP.\n -->\n</div>","rawContent":"{{External|rs}}\n{{Quick Guide}}\n\n==Details==\n{{Quest details page|Shades of Mort'ton}}\n\n==Walkthrough==\n===Start===\n{{Checklist|\n*Enter the ruined house in the south-west of [[Mort'ton]]. Search the shelf on the wall. '''Read the diary'''. After reading the diary, the quest is started and you are able to create [[Serum 207]].\n*If you didn't bring [[Tarromin potion (unf)]]: Pick up the empty vials (can be filled in the house north-east) and search the smashed table for 2 tarromin and one [[rogue's purse]].\n}}\n===Serum 207===\n{{Checklist|\n*Make two [[Serum 207]] by adding clean tarromin to a vial of water and then adding ashes.\n*Use one dose on [[Razmire]] (afflicted) in the general store. {{Chat option|4What are all these shadowy creatures?|1Yes, I'll dispatch those dark and evil creatures.}} (Recommended to '''not''' use official Mort'ton temple World 377 yet to not get interrupted talking to the NPCs, until the step with repairing.)\n*Kill five loar shades and pick up their remains. '''Note:''' any shades that you killed before talking to Razmire will not count.\n*Return to Razmire and give him the remains. He may require more Serum 207.\n*Right click and open his General store, buy an Olive oil.\n*Open his builders' store, buy 5 timber beams, 5 limestone bricks, 25 swamp paste and optionally a [[Flamtaer hammer]].\n*Use the serum on [[Ulsquire Shauncy]], located in the house east of the general store. Talk to him with Loar Remains.\n*Talk to him '''again''' and ask about the remains and the temple. {{Chat option|1What did you find out about the remains?|2What can you tell me about that temple?}}\n}}\n===Repairing the temple===\n{{Checklist|\n*Head north-east of Mort'ton and repair the temple until you reach 100% repair and at least 20 sanctity. (Recommended to use official world 377.)\n*Light the sacred altar in the centre of the temple (or wait until someone else lights it if you don't have level 5 firemaking)\n*Use your olive oil on the flame to make [[sacred oil]].\n*(Recommended) Use Serum 207 on the flame to make [[Serum 208]], which permanently cures NPCs.\n}}\n===Burning a shade===\n{{Checklist|\n*Use the sacred oil on a log to create a [[Pyre logs|pyre log]].\n*Head west of Mort'ton general store, to any grouping of 4 stone funeral pyres. Use the pyre log, then Loar remains on a [[Shades of Mort'ton (minigame)#Cremating the Shades|funeral pyre]]. \n*Light the funeral pyre. '''Warning''': This will grant 25 Prayer XP.\n*Collect the reward.\n*(Recommended) Use the Serum 208 on Razmire.\n*Use the Serum 208 on Ulsquire and finish the dialogue.\n}}\n'''Quest complete!'''\n\n==Rewards==\n{{Quest rewards page|Shades of Mort'ton}}\n\n{{Shades of Mort'ton}}"}